                <p><strong>TDS / TCS deposit (Challan ITNS-281)</strong> is due 7th of every month (30 April for March). <strong>GSTR-1 (outward supplies)</strong> is due 11th of every month for monthly filers. <strong>GSTR-3B (summary return and tax payment)</strong> is due 20th monthly for turnover above Rs 5 crore; 24th quarterly under QRMP for turnover up to Rs 5 crore (Category Y). Patron tracks each against your books so nothing is reconstructed after the fact. Call <a href="tel:+919459456700">+91 94594 56700</a> to set up a filing-reminder schedule.</p>

